odels which neglect the runaway component. The\nresults depend on the injected beam flux density, the temperature and density\nof the background plasma.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2021 17:36:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
