ystems and gravitational\nwave source populations for LIGO, VIRGO, KAGRA, and LISA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2021 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 04:50:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
