les is\nfound to decrease with increasing zinc-atom fraction, a trend which is\nwell-known also for the bulk phase diagram of brass.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2021 20:43:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 06:55:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-22"}
