 campaigns with optical, radio,\nand X-ray observatories can help discriminate further between the competing\nphysical models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2021 23:37:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Apr 2021 13:14:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
