thers' experiences is\nshared. TI dominates immediate inference, which assesses relative rank on\ndirect interactions, because TI could establish social hierarchy more rapidly\napplying information from others' experiences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Mar 2021 10:09:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 3 Apr 2021 17:50:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-06"}
