ween the maximum and minimum values. We conclude that our findings are\nrelevant for coronal hole research from the past decade, and are therefore of\ninterest to the solar and space research community.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Mar 2021 11:20:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
